h and prepare for the demands of the wider world as global citizens. The College takes pride in guiding and encouraging each pupil to fulfil and surpass his or her goals. This is achieved by offering a broad academic curriculum and providing unsurpassed support.</p>\n\n<p>Each pupil will benefit from a structured learning environment with outstanding levels of pastoral care. While at Epsom, they will learn study and time-management skills that will be crucial to success at university.</p>\n\n                  <div class=\"detail-video mb20 center\">\n                    <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/9KVnq6vy7rE\" width=\"640\" height=\"352\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n                  </div><!-- /.detail-video -->\n\n                  <ul class=\"detail-gallery-index thumbnail-images owl-carousel owl-theme owl-loaded\">\n                        <li class=\"detail-gallery-list-item\">\n                          <a class=\"facilities-1\" href=\"https://cdn.international-schools-database.com/system/facility_pictures/images/000/011/666/large/a-level-01.webp?1704891738\" title>\n                            <img title loading=\"lazy\" width=\"200\" height=\"134\" src=\"https://cdn.international-schools-database.com/system/facility_pictures/images/000/011/666/thumb/a-level-01.webp?1704891738\">\n                          </a>\n                        </li>\n                        <li class=\"detail-gallery-list-item\">\n                          <a class=\"facilities-1\" href=\"https://cdn.international-schools-database.com/system/facility_pictures/images/000/011/667/large/a-level-02.webp?1704891740\" title>\n                            <img title loading=\"lazy\" width=\"200\" height=\"134\" src=\"https://cdn.international-schools-database.com/system/facility_pictures/images/000/011/667/thumb/a-level-02.webp?1704891740\">\n                          </a>\n                        </li>\n                        <li class=\"detail-ga